Additional details

Introducing the Diva smart dimmer switch for Caseta smart lighting. Lutron's #1 dimmer is now smart and works with your existing Caseta products. Match existing Diva LED+ dimmer switches in your home with the same elegant, recognized paddle style, updated to match existing Caseta products with an LED-backlit light bar. Welcome Home to Peace of Mind - always come back to a well-lit home with the Diva smart dimmer switch. Enable the Smart Away feature to randomly turn lights on and off to make it look like you're home, even if you're away (smart hub required). Use the smart hub to connect your Diva smart dimmer switch to more leading smart home devices - including Alexa, Apple Home, Google Home, Ring, and Sonos - than any other smart lighting control brand. Not only does the smart hub unlock smart control and device integration - but it also doesn't use Wi-Fi to control your lights. Stay connected even when your Wi-Fi goes down and stop slowing your internet speed with more devices. Flexible Wiring Options: Create a new 3-way or replace an existing one with the Diva smart dimmer switch. Pair a Pico remote and bracket to your dimmer switch and mount the Pico/bracket on almost any surface - no cutting holes or pulling wire requires (Pico and bracket sold separately). The Diva smart dimmer switch has flexible wiring options and does not require a neutral wire. Includes (2) Diva smart dimmer switches with wire label stickers; coordinating wallplate and other accessories sold separately.

      This is a modal window.

      Casta Smart Home Lighting Control

      Diva Smart Dimmer

      Lutron's #1 dimmer is now smart! Match existing Diva LED dimmers in your home with the same rocker-style, updated with an LED-backlit light bar.

      Claro Smart Switch

      Lutron's most popular switch design is now smart. Match existing rocker switches in your home. Soft press paddle switch and an LED indicator light.

      Original Smart Dimmer

      Casta by Lutron's original smart dimmer with contemporary push buttons to dim, brighten and turn on/off.

      Original Smart Switch

      Casta by Lutron's original smart switch design features a simple on/off button in a modern aesthetic.

      • Is a Lutron Smart Hub needed to utilize the smart features?

        Yes, using the Lutron Smart Hub is the key to delivering the best smart lighting experience. When connecting the hub to your router, it creates a fast and reliable connection without interfering or slow down your Wi-Fi.

      • Where can you add a second switch?

        Anywhere! The Pico Remote can be mounted to the wall and connect to any Diva Smart Dimmer to give you multiple switches for one light.

      • Do I need the Smart Hub to use the Diva Smart Dimmer switch and Pico remote together?

        No, Smart dimmers and Pico remotes will still work as normal dimmer switches without buying the Smart Hub. The Smart Hub does unlock auto off, smart scenes, smart away, schedules, and being able to control through the app or voice assistant devices.

      • Can this control two separate lights in the same room?

        Yes, you can connect your Lutron smart dimmer and Pico remote to multiple lights in a room.

      • What happens if I have issues setting up my dimmer switch?

        Our Lutron Support team is one call away and is dedicated to walking you through any issues.
